name: Flower Fawn
description: This artwork was inspired by the sculptures of the Living Forest of Ordino, in Andorra. That forest had a local sculptor pass through since I was last there... It's now got trees with hands attached asking for a ride, heads and entire bodies emerging from the trees, as well as several other rather striking features to see when you just expect a walk in the woods !
